headline: Boston Scientific resumes PFA trial in new patient group after pausing enrollment
summary: Boston Scientific expects to complete enrollment in the coming months in the study comparing pulsed field ablation to anti-arrhythmic drugs in patients with persistent AFib, a spokesperson said.
